{"tid":989450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"炫耀曾殺害1歲半男嬰　兇手出獄後被憤怒鄰居砍死","createTime":"2019-01-21T01:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T13:34:33.000Z","uid":28765,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4af086737b249f0bfc6d6ef91d209d1ca52f024c","tid":989450,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T01:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190120/640_907200543636afe29ed0d564874bdd37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190120%2F640_907200543636afe29ed0d564874bdd37.jpg&h=04c5bf23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n17個月大的男嬰石智明30多年前被母親同居男友虐殺致死。翻攝《太陽報》<br />\n英國一名殺嬰兇手服刑32年後前年出獄，但他竟毫無悔意，還拿被自己殺害的嬰兒開玩笑，鄰居得知後憤而將其砍殺百刀致死。<br />\n <br />\n54歲的高特（David Gaut）30多年前狠心虐殺同居女友的17個月大幼子，他因此遭判無期徒刑，但於前年11月獲假釋出獄。沒想到高特出獄後毫無悔意，在一間中餐廳點外賣時被人聽到他高談闊論的說：「我不喜歡中國食物，但想點一個『石智明』（音譯︰Chi Ming Shek）」，而他所指的石智明，就是被他殘忍虐殺的男嬰。<br />\n <br />\n居民聽見後開始上網搜尋高特和「石智明」的關聯性，驚訝發現高特竟然是殺嬰兇手。和高特住在同一地點的3名男子得知後決定執行「私法正義」，先將高特誘騙到家中，接著用利刃向他猛刺150多刀，在高特死後，這3人還拔掉他的指甲。<br />\n <br />\n高特遭殺害一案發生在去年8月，法官最近開庭審理。被告律師在庭上強調，3名當事人是因為被死者吹噓自己殺嬰惡行而憤怒殺人。其中一名被告則坦承自己有吸毒習慣。目前案件仍在審理當中。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190120/640_67a642fa6d4738da68b94ecb279c6cc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190120%2F640_67a642fa6d4738da68b94ecb279c6cc8.jpg&h=7d8eed1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3名被告在法庭上坦承被死者吹噓殺嬰激怒。翻攝BBC<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190120/1503936/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190120%2F1503936%2F&d=7FZwGubSg%2Boc5%2FIyI3je926kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=af997253\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190120%2F1503936%2F&h=027b5b15\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190120/1503936/</a>"},{"pid":"4db28f69cddef883888febcb64f4929d6b461b15","tid":989450,"uid":20066,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T01:12:55.000Z","msg":"好鄰居<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04cf62452e8abdbf5d6cf38d0f240b17abb9edb","tid":989450,"uid":106986,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T01:12:57.000Z","msg":"和高特住在同一地點的3名男子得知後決定執行「私法正義」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb0514d92c51e85e6dbb577c1295ec8cd934855","tid":989450,"uid":87511,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T01:15:51.000Z","msg":"異能仨"},{"pid":"5610a56d50a031547739f22b50043ac9abaaa75a","tid":989450,"uid":195570,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T01:17:58.000Z","msg":"有時坐監都唔足以令呢d人反省<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0113d70f6467d444816c09d10bdd27933108c4cd","tid":989450,"uid":203543,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T01:18:19.000Z","msg":"雖然嚟三個都係痴線佬，但係絕對好過殺BB個個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d120587254b6126ea8c291717cd56ca14ca2c80","tid":989450,"uid":25345,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T01:18:52.000Z","msg":"若未傷害夠,就用一對手"},{"pid":"9682a26eb33e40262d0cb0ecc15aeae272e621df","tid":989450,"uid":118758,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T01:20:08.000Z","msg":"明明係唔識 衹不過係鄰居 都會咁撚正義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba08ad8c8ea45f574b26ce6177de5dc36be1b237","tid":989450,"uid":53466,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T01:20:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea93baef333b1283051187eaa86eceba4153dbe8","tid":989450,"uid":57186,